## User shorthand (Docit plugin)

| Shorthand | Same as |
|-----------|---------|
| **`-doc`** | **`/docit:doc`** — write this session to `.claude/documents/` and append section 11 to **`agents.md`**. |
| **`-docup`** or **`-docitup`** | **`/docit:up`** — read existing Docit summaries, match the user’s bug or question, then investigate using those paths and structure. |
| **`-doclist`** | **`/docit:list`** — list indexed summaries under `.claude/documents/`. |

Treat these as the only instruction when the message is exactly the shorthand (or starts with it with no other task). No separate API — use this session and files on disk as the source.
